<library name="SparkFun-PowerSymbols" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:library:530">
<description>&lt;h3&gt;SparkFun Power Symbols&lt;/h3&gt;
This library contains power, ground, and voltage-supply symbols.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
