<deviceset name="SWD-5PIN" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:41390532/1" library_version="2">
<description>&lt;h1&gt;5-pin SWD connector&lt;/h1&gt;

Test-point based header for SWD. 
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 1 - PWR
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 2 - SWDIO
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 3 - SWCLK
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 4 - NC
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 5 - GND
&lt;br&gt;
Pin 6 - RESET</description>
<gates>
<gate name="G$1" symbol="CONN_03X2_NO4" x="0" y="0"/>
</gates>
